## Apennines region hosts 8 karst springs from Italy.

The karst spring discharge data are provided by 
Christian Massari (christian.massari@cnr.it), 
Marco Dionigi (marco.dionigi@cnr.it), 
Lucio Di Matteo (lucio.dimatteo@unipg.it), 
Daniela Valigi (daniela.valigi@unipg.it), 
Davide Fronzi (d.fronzi@staff.univpm.it).

The provided data belong to 3 different institutions:

CNR - National Research Council of Italy "https://www.cnr.it/en".
Umbria Regional Hydrometeorological Service "https://apps.arpa.umbria.it/acqua/contenuto/portata-delle-Sorgenti".
Marche REGIONAL WEATHER-HYDRO-RAINMETRIC INFORMATION SYSTEM "http://app.protezionecivile.marche.it/sol/contatti.sol?lang=it".

For more information, please see Metadata table.
